Program: Omnibus
Title: The International Missing Persons Conference and Register
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376l0t
Last Broadcast Date: 24 April 1995
'No one knows how many people are missing'. Speaking to people who have lost relatives and attending the conference which is trying to establish an international register of missing persons and to find ways of providing support for friends and relatives of the missing.